WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.340 --> 00:00:03.960
If you want the house, you can have it. Just sign these papers.

2
00:00:03.960 --> 00:00:11.849
Why the rush? It's late. Why don't we... enjoy the night?

3
00:00:16.030 --> 00:00:19.629
What'd you put in that water?

4
00:00:19.629 --> 00:00:23.730
Just a little something to help us. Relax.

5
00:00:23.730 --> 00:00:28.730
We're married. You can do whatever you want with me.

6
00:00:28.730 --> 00:00:29.730
I want you to leave. Now!

7
00:00:29.730 --> 00:00:32.729
I'm your wife! You can't just kick me out!

8
00:00:32.729 --> 00:00:38.899
Fine. You stay. I'm leaving.

9
00:00:38.899 --> 00:00:50.679
Damn it! Everything is a mess.

10
00:00:50.679 --> 00:00:53.679
My marriage is a record, Lydia is missing, and...

11
00:00:53.679 --> 00:00:58.780
Mr. Hart...

12
00:00:58.780 --> 00:01:06.109
Ugh, I can't stop thinking about him. How does he feel about me?

13
00:01:06.109 --> 00:01:18.099
Mr. Hart, what are you doing here?

